title: Fauci Steps Down, Space Bros Go On Hiatus | Daily Best of August 23 | Rick & Bubba
description:
Dr. Anthony Fauci announces his plans to step down from his government job, so we take a look at some of his greatest "accomplishments." Bubba is not at the studio today because of some abdominal pain last night and is being looked at by doctors. Unfortunately, this means Bubba and Adler will not be Space Bros and travel to see the upcoming NASA rocket launch this weekend. MLB star Albert Pujols hits his 693rd career home run. And lastly, a Yankees fan drinks a beer through a hotdog straw.
